Game.....: The Last Blade 2: Heart Of The Samurai
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: August 9th, 2001
Ripped.......: Nothing

Release Notes
A Samurai's honor is found at the edge of his blade! Last Blade 2 
is a 2P-VS fighting game where legendary Japanese Samurais gather 
for a fight to the death. There is a total of 16 different 
characters, each with their own characteristics, weapons and 
traits. Features: Story Mode, VS Mode, Time Attack, Training Mode, 
Art Gallery and Demo Gallery. 